    "multirow_AxmcVr": {
      "type": "multirow",
      "blocks": {
        "row_tNxtwH": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/BD895B0B-B369-437E-AD6F-167EFEA8F6B7.jpg",
            "image_alt": "",
            "caption": "Straps Are Outdated",
            "heading": "WHY CHOOSE VSLING?",
            "text": "<p>Vsling® is the upgrade hunters have been waiting for:</p><p>➤ Silent elastic carry system</p><p>➤ Elastic Stability Advantage — constant tension, steadier Binos.</p><p>➤ Faster sling-to-shoot transitions</p><p>➤ More comfortable all-day carry</p><p>➤ Hands-free movement in the field </p><p>➤ Shoot With Sling On</p><p></p><p></p><h2>A BETTER DESIGN</h2><p>The 100% elastic Vsling® keeps your bow <strong>comfortably snug</strong> to your body. No more floppy straps slapping, snagging, or slowing you down. It's sleek, quiet, and simple - designed so you can move from carry to full draw in seconds. Explore the <a href=\"/products/bow-sling\" title=\"Vsling Hands-Free Compound Bow Sling\">hands-free Vsling compound bow sling</a>, <a href=\"/products/vsling-crossbow-gun-sling\" title=\"Vsling Crossbow Sling\">crossbow sling</a>, and <a href=\"/products/vsling-bino-sling\" title=\"Vsling Bino Sling\">bino sling</a>.</p>",
            "button_label": "UPGRADE TODAY",
            "button_link": "shopify://collections/all"
          }
        },
        "row_hC89Qa": {
          "type": "row",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2ABF8D9A-4D02-4310-BA48-EAFA7D8055C9.jpg",
            "image_alt": "",
            "caption": "The Future of Bow Carrying",
            "heading": "THE GAME CHANGER",
            "text": "<h3>SHOOT WITH THE SLING ON</h3><p>Unlike old slings that must be unclipped or removed before shooting, Patent Pending Vsling® is engineered so you can draw and shoot instantly without taking it off. This \"always-ready\" design keeps your muscles relaxed and your focus sharp. </p><p></p><h3>HANDS FREE COMFORT</h3><p>Think of it like a baby carrier for your bow - comfortable, balanced, and freeing your hands for glassing, climbing, or calling. The elastic stretch makes long hikes easier while keeping your bow tight and ready. Crossbow hunters can run the same system with the <a href=\"/products/vsling-crossbow-gun-sling\" title=\"Vsling Crossbow Sling\">Vsling crossbow sling</a>, and glass hands-free with the <a href=\"/products/vsling-bino-sling\" title=\"Vsling Bino Sling\">Vsling bino sling</a>.</p>",
            "button_label": "SHOP VSLING®",
            "button_link": "shopify://collections/all"
          }
        }
      },
