        "column_8df3iM": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/4.png",
            "image_alt": "",
            "title": "Easy Installation & Custom Fit",
            "text": "<p>Installing the Vsling® is simple and intuitive. The final step uses a snug double knot, which not only secures the sling but also makes it effortless to fine-tune. Let the elasticity do the work! This design allows for quick, mindless adjustments to perfectly match any body type, hunting style, or carry preference. No complicated buckles or clips which allows for a clean custom fit every time.<br/><br/></p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        },
        "column_rHMmbY": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2.png",
            "image_alt": "",
            "title": "The Last Sling You'll Ever Need",
            "text": "<p>Hunters don't settle for outdated gear. Just like the shift from wood arrows to carbon, it's time to leave floppy slings behind. The Vsling® Bow Sling is the hands-free, always-ready, shoot-with-it-on solution every bowhunter needs. <a href=\"/products/bow-sling\" title=\"Vsling Shoot-Ready Bow Sling\">Shop the shoot-ready elastic bow sling</a>.</p>",
            "link_label": "",
            "link": ""
          }
        }
